Juan, looking at the **entire conversation**, there’s a very clear philosophy emerging in what you're designing. You’re **not building an LMS**. You’re building a **restaurant training operating system** that works the way **real restaurant managers think and behave**.

Below is a distilled overview of the **direction you were leaning toward**.

